CHAEL B.):</strong></span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="h.305c47797de324fe_1435" class="yaqOZd" style=""><div class="IFuOkc"></div><div class="mYVXT"><div class="LS81yb VICjCf" tabindex="-1"><div class="hJDwNd-AhqUyc-R6PoUb purZT-AhqUyc-R6PoUb pSzOP-AhqUyc-R6PoUb JNdkSc"><div class="JNdkSc-SmKAyb"><div class="" jscontroller="sGwD4d" jsaction="zXBUYb:zTPCnb;zQF9Uc:Qxe3nd;" jsname="F57UId"><div class="oKdM2c Kzv0Me"><div id="h.305c47797de324fe_1438" class="hJDwNd-AhqUyc-R6PoUb purZT-AhqUyc-R6PoUb pSzOP-AhqUyc-R6PoUb jXK9ad D2fZ2 OjCsFc wHaque"><div class="jXK9ad-SmKAyb"><div class="tyJCtd baZpAe"><div class="t3iYD"><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/H6hrZRJpd7SDU4CS0Rdx3nGSYxM_GLJ79NtYcjG6SOYZbA06CC5HKrKaKckN25POyBQDng=w1280" class="CENy8b" role="img" style="width: 100%; margin: 0% 0 0% 0%"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="hJDwNd-AhqUyc-OwsYgb purZT-AhqUyc-II5mzb pSzOP-AhqUyc-qWD73c JNdkSc"><div class="JNdkSc-SmKAyb"><div class="" jscontroller="sGwD4d" jsaction="zXBUYb:zTPCnb;zQF9Uc:Qxe3nd;" jsname="F57UId"><div class="oKdM2c Kzv0Me"><div id="h.305c47797de324fe_1441" class="hJDwNd-AhqUyc-OwsYgb jXK9ad D2fZ2 OjCsFc wHaque GNzUNc"><div class="jXK9ad-SmKAyb"><div class="tyJCtd mGzaTb baZpAe"><p dir="ltr" class="CDt4Ke zfr3Q"><span style="font-family: &#39;Lato&#39;;"><strong>Using </strong></span><span class=" aw5Odc" style="font-family: &#39;Lato&#39;; text-decoration: underline;"><a class="XqQF9c" href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3schools.com%2F&amp;sa=D&amp;sntz=1&amp;usg=AFQjCNG8yt92PSM1MxvgXMjl47ulgcFCyw" target="_blank"><strong>Hypertext Markup Language (HTML)</strong></a></span><span style="font-family: &#39;Lato&#39;;"><strong>, we can opt not to include information in the web address.</strong></span></p><p dir="ltr" class="CDt4Ke zfr3Q"><span style="font-family: &#39;Lato&#39;;"><strong>Example Usage: When we submit a login form, we prefer that the username and password are not included in the web address.</strong></span></p><p dir="ltr" class="CDt4Ke zfr3Q"><span style="font-family: &#39;Lato&#39;;"><strong>We can execute this action using HTML&#39;s POST command, instead of the GET command.</strong></span></p><p dir="ltr" class="CDt4Ke zfr3Q"><span style="font-family: &#39;Lato&#39;;"><strong>Because we have access to the web page instructions, e.g. which page to load after submitting the login form, we can add instructions to receive the username and password sent using the POST command.</strong></span></p><p dir="ltr" class="CDt4Ke zfr3Q"><span style="font-family: &#39;Lato&#39;;"><strong>I verified that unauthorized access to web pages via the network is a technique used by the  budol-budol/manloloko/carnapper/cybercriminal/communist terrorist group to steal information to quickly get money.</strong></span></p><p dir="ltr" class="CDt4Ke zfr3Q"><span style="font-family: &#39;Lato&#39;;"><strong>Recommended Action:</strong></span></p><p dir="ltr" class="CDt4Ke zfr3Q"><span style="font-family: &#39;Lato&#39;;"><strong>1) learn: </strong></span><span class=" aw5Odc" style="font-family: &#39;Lato&#39;; text-decoration: underline;"><a class="XqQF9c" href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fusbong%2Fdocumentation%2Ftree%2Fmaster%2FUsbong%2Fcompany%2FHR%2FUsbong%2520Education%2520Training%2520Courses%2FIntroduction%2520to%2520Writing%2520Pages%2520Using%2520HTML%2Fres&amp;sa=D&amp;sntz=1&amp;usg=AFQjCNFUZMIgGrdqrCCuXZl2D9l9846-CQ" target="_blank"><strong>Usbong Training: Introduction to Writing Pages Using HTML</strong></a></span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="hJDwNd-AhqUyc-II5mzb JNdkSc L6cTce-purZT L6cTce-pSzOP"><div class="JNdkSc-SmKAyb"><div class="" jscontroller="sGwD4d" jsaction="zXBUYb:zTPCnb;zQF9Uc:Qxe3nd;" jsname="F57UId"></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="h.305c47797de324fe_1442" class="yaqOZd" style=""><div class="IFuOkc"></div><div class="mYVX